      "content": "exactly. i just feel like it's more than just silence. ever since i got the new office, i've noticed people from compliance or internal audit \"dropping by\" my floor way more often. it's like they're trying to keep tabs on me under the guise of \"welcoming\" me to the new role. i'm starting to feel like my every move is being watched. do you think they've redirected some of the surveillance resources toward my department specifically?",
